---
/**
 * InviteReturnContract — "O retorno é o artefato acionável" pattern explainer
 *
 * Renders three sub-sections for the v0.1.0 docsite roadmap page:
 *   1. Invite card — MCP App tool-result widget mockup with copy button
 *   2. Application-layer return contract — JSON code block + annotation
 *   3. Pattern opportunity table — use-case × return mapping, versioned badges
 *
 * Design references:
 *   - Linear.app: elevation via lightness delta, dense without crowding
 *   - Vercel docs: code block with dark tinted bg, tabular data layout
 *   - EventStormingBoard / UseCaseMatrix color tokens (same page): consistency
 *
 * Color tokens (OKLCH — perceptually uniform):
 *   Emerald accent  oklch(0.72 0.17 162)  → #10b981 sRGB fallback
 *   Blue accent     oklch(0.70 0.14 240)  → #5B9BD5 sRGB fallback
 *   Amber accent    oklch(0.82 0.16 80)   → #f59e0b sRGB fallback
 *   Page base bg    #0b1a15               (consistent with board components)
 *
 * Constraints:
 *   - This file is an .astro component, NOT MDX → <style> is valid here (scoped)
 *   - Copy button uses <script> in this .astro file — safe from MDX acorn parser
 *   - All client JS in a single <script> block, no external deps
 *   - prefers-reduced-motion respected
 *   - WCAG 2.2: contrast ≥ 4.5:1 on all text, focus-visible ring on interactive elements
 */
---

<!-- Invite Card -->
<div class="irc-invite-wrap">
  <p class="irc-tool-eyebrow">
    <span class="irc-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    MCP Operacional &nbsp;·&nbsp; Resultado da ferramenta
  </p>

  <div class="irc-invite-card" role="region" aria-label="Card de convite — Casa da Mata São Vicente">
    <div class="irc-card-header">
      <span class="irc-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌿</span>
      <div class="irc-card-title-block">
        <span class="irc-card-type-label">Convite</span>
        <strong class="irc-card-title">Casa da Mata São Vicente</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="irc-card-body">
      <p class="irc-salutation">Olá <strong>Thiago</strong>, sua associação está provisionada no <span class="irc-brand">canna-br</span>. Você é o administrador inicial (<span class="irc-role">Diretor</span>).</p>

      <div class="irc-credential-block" aria-label="Credencial temporária de primeiro acesso">
        <p class="irc-cred-label">
          <span aria-hidden="true">🔑</span> Primeiro acesso (credencial temporária):
        </p>
        <dl class="irc-cred-dl">
          <div class="irc-cred-row">
            <dt>Login</dt>
            <dd><code>thiago@casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org</code></dd>
          </div>
          <div class="irc-cred-row">
            <dt>Senha</dt>
            <dd><code>thiago@casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org</code> <span class="irc-cred-note">(igual ao login)</span></dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <p class="irc-link-row">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🔗</span> Entrar:&nbsp;
        <span class="irc-link-pill">https://casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org</span>
      </p>

      <p class="irc-expire-note">No 1º login você define a senha real + ativa 2FA. A credencial temporária expira em <strong>7 dias</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="irc-card-actions">
      <button
        type="button"
        class="irc-copy-btn"
        aria-label="Copiar convite para a área de transferência"
        data-copy-text={"🌿 Convite — Casa da Mata São Vicente\n\nOlá Thiago, sua associação está provisionada no canna-br. Você é o administrador inicial (Diretor).\n\n🔑 Primeiro acesso (credencial temporária):\n   Login:  thiago@casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org\n   Senha:  thiago@casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org   (igual ao login)\n\n🔗 Entrar:  https://casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org\n\nNo 1º login você define a senha real + ativa 2FA. A credencial temporária expira em 7 dias."}
      >
        <svg class="irc-copy-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="irc-copy-label">Copiar convite</span>
      </button>
      <div class="irc-copy-toast" role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Return Contract -->
<div class="irc-contract-wrap">
  <div class="irc-code-block" role="region" aria-label="Contrato de retorno da camada de aplicação — JSON">
    <div class="irc-code-header">
      <span class="irc-code-lang">json</span>
      <span class="irc-code-filename">provision_association + seed_admin_user → output</span>
    </div>
    <pre class="irc-pre"><code class="irc-code">{`{
  "association": {
    "id": "assoc_…",
    "slug": "casa-da-mata-sv",
    "name": "Casa da Mata São Vicente",
    "tenant": "casa-da-mata-sv"
  },
  "admin": {
    "name": "Thiago",
    "role": "Diretor",
    "login": "thiago@casa-da-mata-sv.cannabr.org",
    "must_change_credentials": true,
    "expires_at": "2026-06-18T00:00:00Z"
  },
  "invite": {
    "subject": "Convite — Casa da Mata São Vicente no cannabr.org",
    "body_markdown": "…",
    "body_plain": "…",
    "copy_paste": "🌿 Convite — Casa da Mata São Vicente …"
  }
}`}</code></pre>
  </div>
  <p class="irc-contract-note">
    A chamada foi <code>provision_association</code> + <code>seed_admin_user</code> via o MCP Operacional; o campo que importa para a UX é <code>invite.copy_paste</code>.
  </p>
</div>

<!-- Pattern Opportunity Table -->
<div class="irc-table-wrap" role="region" aria-label="Tabela: o retorno é o artefato acionável — oportunidades por use case">
  <table class="irc-table" aria-label="Pattern: o retorno é o artefato acionável">
    <caption class="irc-table-caption">
      Cada use case devolve hoje apenas o registro. A coluna "Devia devolver" mostra o artefato agent-first que fecha o loop para o operador ou membro.
    </caption>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col" class="irc-th irc-th--usecase">Use Case</th>
        <th scope="col" class="irc-th irc-th--today">Devolve hoje</th>
        <th scope="col" class="irc-th irc-th--artifact">Devia devolver (artefato)</th>
        <th scope="col" class="irc-th irc-th--version">Versão</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr class="irc-tr">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">provision / seed_admin</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">ids</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">convite admin <em>copy-paste</em></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v01">v0.1.0</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">reset_credential</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">ok</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">mensagem "nova senha temporária" pronta</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v01">v0.1.0</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">registerMember</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">member id</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">boas-vindas + link de 1º acesso do membro (WhatsApp-ready) + carteirinha digital</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v01">v0.1.0</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">viewMemberQuota</code> <span class="irc-context">(perto do limite)</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">número</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">nudge "40/45g este mês" pro membro</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v01">v0.1.0</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><span class="irc-uc irc-uc--prose">1º login concluído</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">—</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">coach "bem-vindo · próximos 3 passos"</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v01">v0.1.0</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr irc-tr--v2">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">recordDispensation</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">event</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">recibo de dispensação pro paciente (PDF / texto)</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v02">v0.2</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr irc-tr--v2">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">generate_traceability_report</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">data</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">relatório pronto pro grupo da diretoria</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v02">v0.2</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr irc-tr--v2">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">submit_sngpc</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">protocolo</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">confirmação de protocolo copy-paste</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v02">v0.2</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr irc-tr--v2">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><code class="irc-uc">explain_compliance_gap</code></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">gaps</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">checklist de remediação acionável</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v02">v0.2</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="irc-tr irc-tr--v2">
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--usecase"><span class="irc-uc irc-uc--prose">membership / prescrição expirando</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--today"><span class="irc-muted">—</span></td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--artifact">lembrete de renovação pronto</td>
        <td class="irc-td irc-td--version"><span class="irc-badge irc-badge--v02">v0.2</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<style>
  /* ================================================================
     SHARED TOKENS — consistent with EventStormingBoard + UseCaseMatrix
  ================================================================ */
  .irc-invite-wrap,
  .irc-contract-wrap,
  .irc-table-wrap {
    --irc-bg:            #0b1a15;
    --irc-border:        rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.22);
    --irc-border-row:    rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.09);
    --irc-emerald:       #10b981;
    --irc-emerald-300:   #6ee7b7;
    --irc-emerald-dim:   rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.14);
    --irc-blue:          #5B9BD5;
    --irc-blue-300:      #bdd9f7;
    --irc-amber:         #f59e0b;
    --irc-amber-300:     #fde68a;
    --irc-text:          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    --irc-muted:         rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    --irc-micro:         rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32);
    --irc-font-mono:     var(--sl-font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace);
    --irc-font-ui:       var(--sl-font, system-ui, sans-serif);
    --irc-motion-enter:  cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --irc-motion-state:  cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    font-family: var(--irc-font-ui);
  }

  /* ================================================================
     1. INVITE CARD WIDGET
  ================================================================ */
  .irc-invite-wrap {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  /* Tool-result eyebrow — looks like a terminal output label */
  .irc-tool-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0 0 8px 2px;
  }

  .irc-dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--irc-emerald);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: irc-dot-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes irc-dot-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
    50%       { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .irc-invite-card {
    background: var(--irc-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--irc-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    /* Linear card elevation: lightness delta rather than shadow */
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  /* Card header — icon + title */
  .irc-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--irc-border);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
  }

  .irc-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .irc-card-title-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .irc-card-type-label {
    font-size: 0.5625rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .irc-card-title {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* Card body */
  .irc-card-body {
    padding: 16px 16px 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .irc-salutation {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--irc-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .irc-salutation strong {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
  }

  .irc-brand {
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .irc-role {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.14);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.28);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0 5px;
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Credential block */
  .irc-credential-block {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.14);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
  }

  .irc-cred-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .irc-cred-dl {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .irc-cred-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 44px 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .irc-cred-row dt {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--irc-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .irc-cred-row dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .irc-cred-row dd code {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10);
    color: #6ee7b7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.20);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .irc-cred-note {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--irc-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Link row */
  .irc-link-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--irc-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .irc-link-pill {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--irc-blue-300);
    background: rgba(91, 155, 213, 0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(91, 155, 213, 0.22);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  /* Expiry note */
  .irc-expire-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.52);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .irc-expire-note strong {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* Card actions */
  .irc-card-actions {
    padding: 10px 16px 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.09);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .irc-copy-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 7px 14px;
    min-height: 36px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.38);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10);
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    font-family: var(--irc-font-ui);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition:
      background 0.15s var(--irc-motion-state),
      border-color 0.15s var(--irc-motion-state),
      transform 0.15s var(--irc-motion-state);
  }

  .irc-copy-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.18);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.65);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .irc-copy-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .irc-copy-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--irc-emerald);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .irc-copy-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .irc-copy-label {
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Toast */
  .irc-copy-toast {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--irc-emerald-300);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--irc-motion-enter);
    pointer-events: none;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.28);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .irc-copy-toast.irc-toast-visible {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* ================================================================
     2. RETURN CONTRACT CODE BLOCK
  ================================================================ */
  .irc-contract-wrap {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    /* Gen-UI overflow contract #16 */
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .irc-code-block {
    background: var(--irc-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--irc-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .irc-code-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 7px 14px;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--irc-border);
  }

  .irc-code-lang {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.5625rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.55);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.20);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 1px 5px;
  }

  .irc-code-filename {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    color: var(--irc-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .irc-pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
  }

  /* Override Starlight's default <pre> styling within our component */
  .irc-code-block .irc-pre {
    background: transparent !important;
    padding: 14px 18px !important;
    border: none !important;
    border-radius: 0 !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }

  .irc-code {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    display: block;
    white-space: pre;
    background: transparent !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
  }

  .irc-contract-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--irc-muted);
    margin: 10px 0 0 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 2px;
  }

  .irc-contract-note code {
    font-family: var(--irc-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10);
    color: #6ee7b7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.20);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1px 5px;
  }

  /* ================================================================
     3. PATTERN OPPORTUNITY TABLE
  ================================================================ */
  .irc-table-wrap {
    /* Gen-UI overflow contract #16 */
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow-x: auto;
